{
  "stem": "1895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I want to mention another thing about Auschwitz which I think is important.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most Sundays, hangings took place in the main square of Camp D in Auschwitz, where I was stationed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the hangings, they had a tremendous orchestra, with probably the best musicians in Europe at the time, because as the-- as the trains arrived, the first questions that the SS asked, are there any musicians here?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would pluck them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had accumulated probably the best musicians in the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had an orchestra, which comprised at least 50 to 60 men playing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people were playing every Sunday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They gave concerts after the hangings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In their uniforms?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In their-- you mean in their stripes?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a lectern.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was an orchestra leader.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember there was a cordoned-off section for the Germans, for those who were not inmates who came to listen to the concerts.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know for a fact that the concert couldn't start until the town church let out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a time when the town church let out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had to give these Germans who attended church time to make it the camp so they could listen to the concert.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you understand the implication?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I am turned off to classical music.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I believe I'm turned off to classical music because I constantly associate classical music with these Germans who came to listen to the concert, even from the churches, and enjoyed it so much at a place like Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In November of 1947-- May I ask, would it be-- was it your opinion at that time that the townspeople knew what was going on?",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
